00:05:16.179 --> 00:05:20.140
and the religious leaders are threatening the disciples,

00:05:20.140 --> 00:05:22.980
and they're saying, listen, we're commanding you

00:05:22.980 --> 00:05:27.940
not to teach or to even speak in the name of Jesus.

00:05:27.940 --> 00:05:31.339
It tells us that Peter responds in verse 20 and says,

00:05:31.339 --> 00:05:32.959
