00:05:34.779 --> 00:05:37.339
I'm thankful for his boldness.

00:05:37.339 --> 00:05:40.859
It says in verse 21, so when they had further threatened

00:05:40.859 --> 00:05:44.880
them, they let them go, finding nothing

00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:46.940
how they might punish them because of the people,

00:05:46.940 --> 00:05:50.179
for all men glorified God for that which was done.

00:05:50.179 --> 00:05:52.940
It tells us that the man in Acts chapter number three

00:05:52.940 --> 00:05:55.459
was about 40 years old on whom this miracle

00:05:55.459 --> 00:05:57.140
of healing was showed.

00:05:57.140 --> 00:05:59.820
So we find that they commanded them in verse number 18,

00:05:59.820 --> 00:06:02.339
and Peter responds in verse 20,

00:06:02.339 --> 00:06:04.100
and then they threatened them again

00:06:04.100 --> 00:06:07.459
before they released them, and we come to verse number 23

00:06:07.459 --> 00:06:10.260
as our passage for our study this morning.

00:06:10.260 --> 00:06:12.100
The Bible says, and being let go,

00:06:12.100 --> 00:06:14.420
and so these disciples are released

00:06:14.420 --> 00:06:15.679
from the religious leaders.

00:06:15.679 --> 00:06:17.200
