00:07:04.540 --> 00:07:06.500
why did the heathen rage?

00:07:06.500 --> 00:07:09.059
And the people imagined vain things.

00:07:09.059 --> 00:07:11.820
The kings of the earth stood up and the rulers

00:07:11.820 --> 00:07:13.980
were gathered together against the Lord

00:07:13.980 --> 00:07:16.579
and against his Christ for of a truth

00:07:16.579 --> 00:07:19.660
against the holy child, Jesus, whom thou hast anointed,

00:07:19.660 --> 00:07:22.140
both Herod and Pontius Pilate with the Gentiles

00:07:22.140 --> 00:07:24.420
and the people of Israel were gathered together

00:07:24.420 --> 00:07:27.019
for to do whatsoever thy hand and thy counsel

00:07:27.019 --> 00:07:28.899
