00:07:28.899 --> 00:07:33.899
And now, verse 29, and now, Lord, behold their threatenings.

00:07:34.940 --> 00:07:38.500
And grant unto thy servants that with all boldness,

00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:43.019
they may speak thy word by stretching forth thine hand

00:07:43.019 --> 00:07:46.380
to heal that signs and wonders may be done

00:07:46.380 --> 00:07:49.260
by the name of thy holy child, Jesus.

00:07:49.260 --> 00:07:51.859
